searching system

  // mer cragrum hnaravor klini search anel @st hexinaki anvan, @st grqi vernagri, @st grqi entagluxneri vernagreri kam aravel       	  haytni u taracvac barakapakcutyunnerov (ays sur@ vor@ spanec davajan hor@ kspani nayev uracox mor@)
1. video_lesson      // video_lesson-@ canotacnum e user-in cragri tvay entabajnin ev nranic ogtvelu kargi (miayn arajin angam)
2. searching @st hexinaki
3. searching @st grqi vernagri
4. searching @st grqi gluxneri vernagri
5. searching @st barakapakcutyunneri

sign_in system
  
  // grancveluc heto ogtater@ stanum a aravelutyunner chgrancvac useri hamemat
  // grancveluc heto ogtatiroj@ trvum e ir arandzin gradaran@ voroshaki hishoxutyan cavalov
1. video_lesson      // video_lesson-@ canotacnum e user-in cragri tvay entabajnin ev nranic ogtvelu kargi (miayn arajin angam)
2. na karox e ir gradaran upload anel ayn inch kuzi
3. na karox e ogtvel voroshaki aravelutyunneric, baci girq pntrel@, download ev upload anel@ na karox e nayev girq patvirel,         	patvirelu depqum vjarum@ katarvum e bankain classic qarteri mijocov
4. na karox e ogtvel searching system-i aravelutyunneric, grancvac ogtatereri hamar searching katarvum e voch miayn cragri nersum    	ayl nayev online (karox en tesnel te irenc pntrac grqic moataka xanutneric vor mekum ka ev inch arji)
5. aktivutyan tokosner@ mer nshac sandxakin hascnelu depqum ogtater@ karox e ogtvel zexchain hamakargic petveri depqum


